quran[55]{c,v,t}:
  82,1,Igihe ikirere kizasatagurika
  82,2,N’igihe inyenyeri zizanyanyagira
  82,3,N’igihe inyanja zizuzura (amazi yazo akarenga inkombe)
  82,4,N’igihe imva zizabirindurwa (zigakurwamo ibizirimo)
  82,5,(Icyo gihe) umuntu azamenya ibyo yakoze mbere n’ibyo yigijeyo ngo azabe abikora (byaba ibyiza cyangwa ibibi)
  82,6,"Yewe muntu! N’iki cyaguteye kwirengagiza Nyagasani wawe, Nyirubutagatifu"
  82,7,We wakuremye akagutunganya ndetse akanaguha imiterere igukwiye
  82,8,Yaragutunganyije aguha ishusho ashaka
  82,9,Oya! Nyamara muhakana umunsi w’ibihembo
  82,10,Ariko mu by’ukuri mufite ababagenzura (abamalayika babashinzwe)
  82,11,Bubashywe kandi bandika (ibikorwa byanyu byiza n’ibibi)
  82,12,Bazi ibyo mukora byose
  82,13,Mu by’ukuri abakora ibyiza bazaba mu munezero uhambaye (Ijuru)
  82,14,Naho abangizi bazaba mu muriro ugurumana
  82,15,Bazawuhiramo ku munsi w’ibihembo
  82,16,Kandi ntibazigera bawuvamo
  82,17,None se ni iki kizakumenyesha umunsi w’ibihembo
  82,18,"Nanone, ni iki kizakumenyesha umunsi w’ibihembo"
  82,19,"(Uzaba) ari umunsi umuntu atazagira icyo amarira undi, kandi kuri uwo munsi itegeko ryose rizaba ari irya Allah"
  83,1,Ibihano bikomeye bizahanishwa abatuzuza ibipimo
  83,2,"Ba bandi igihe bapimiwe n’abandi bantu, basaba kuzurizwa ibipimo"
  83,3,"Nyamara bo bapimira (abandi), bakabaha ibituzuye"
  83,4,Ese bakeka ko batazazurwa (ngo babazwe)
  83,5,Ku munsi uhambaye
  83,6,Umunsi abantu (bose) bazahagarara imbere ya Nyagasani w’ibiremwa
  83,7,Oya! Mu by’ukuri igitabo cy’inkozi z’ibibi (cyanditsemo ibikorwa byazo) gishyinguwe mu bubiko bwabugenewe bwitwa Sijiini
  83,8,None se ni iki cyakumenyesha Sijiini
  83,9,Ni igitabo cyanditse mu buryo bunoze kandi budasibama
  83,10,Uwo munsi ibihano bikaze bizaba kuri ba bandi bahinyura
  83,11,Ba bandi bahinyura umunsi w’ibihembo
  83,12,Kandi nta wundi uwuhakana usibye urengera (imbibi za Allah) w’umunyabyaha
  83,13,(Wa wundi) usomerwa amagambo yacu (yo muri Qur’an) akavuga ati “Ni inkuru z’abo hambere.”
  83,14,Oya! Ahubwo ibyo bakoraga (ibyaha) byatwikiriye imitima yabo
  83,15,Oya! Mu by’ukuri kuri uwo munsi bazabuzwa kureba Nyagasani wabo
  83,16,Maze bahire mu muriro ugurumana
  83,17,Nuko babwirwe bati “Ibi ni byo mwajyaga muhinyura.”
  83,18,Oya! Mu by’ukuri igitabo cy’abakora ibyiza (cyanditsemo ibikorwa byabo) gishyinguwe mu bubiko bwabugenewe bwitwa Iliyyuuna
  83,19,None se ni iki cyakumenyesha Iliyuna
  83,20,Ni igitabo cyanditse mu buryo bunoze kandi budasibama
  83,21,(Abamalayika) begereye Allah ni bo bazakibera abahamya
  83,22,Mu by’ukuri abakora ibyiza bazaba mu munezero uhambaye (Ijuru)
  83,23,"Bicaye ku bitanda byiza, bitegereza (ibyiza barimo, harimo no kureba uburanga bwa Nyagasani wabo)"
  83,24,Uzabona uburanga bwabo burabagirana kubera ibyishimo
  83,25,Bazahabwa ikinyobwa gipfundikiye
  83,26,"Intama ya nyuma (y’icyo kinyobwa) izaba ifite impumuro y’umubavu wa Miski. Kubera ibyo rero, ngaho abarushanwa nibarushanwe"
  83,27,(Icyo kinyobwa) kizaba kivanze na Tas’niim (amazi y’isoko ituruka mu iriba ryo mu ijuru)
  83,28,Isoko izanyobwaho n’abazaba bari hafi (ya Allah)
  83,29,Mu by’ukuri (ku isi) inkozi z’ibibi zajyaga ziseka abemeramana
  83,30,Bazinyuraho zikabaryanira inzara
  83,31,"Zaba zisubiye mu miryango yazo, zikabagira urwenya"
  83,32,"N’iyo zababonaga, zaravugaga ziti “Mu by’ukuri bariya barayobye.”"
  83,33,Nyamara ntabwo (izo nkozi z’ibibi) zashinzwe kuba abagenzuzi (b’abemeramana)
  83,34,"Ariko uyu munsi, abemeramana ni bo bari buseke abahakanyi"
  83,35,"Bicaye ku bitanda byiza, bitegereza (ibyiza barimo, harimo no kureba uburanga bwa Nyagasani wabo)"
  83,36,Ese abahakanyi ntabwo bahembewe ibyo bajyaga bakora